ENTRY            32601   20260409   20260528   20260528       3223
SUBENT        32601001   20260409   20260528   20260528       3223
BIB                 12         27
TITLE      Cross section measurements for 98Mo(n,a)95Zr,
            95Mo(n,p)95mNb, 95Mo(n,p)95gNb and 181Ta(n,p)181Hf
            reactions
AUTHOR     (Kong Xiangzhong, Wang Yongchang, Yang Jingkang,
            Yuan Junqian, Wang Xuezhi)
INSTITUTE  (3CPRLNZ)
REFERENCE  (J,CNP,14,239,1992)
FACILITY   (CCW,3CPRLNZ) ZF-300-2 intense neutron generator
INC-SOURCE (D-T) Deuteron beam (effective average energy 125 keV,
            beam current ~20 mA) on Ti-T target (~0.9 mg/cm2),
            ~(1-2)*10**12 neutrons/sec
INC-SPECT  Neutron energies determined by cross section ratio of
            90Zr(n,2n)89Zr and 93Nb(n,2n)92mNb
DETECTOR   (HPGE) Coaxial type, relative efficiency 20% and
            energy resolution 3 keV at 1.33 MeV, efficiency
            calibrated with the standard gamma source SRM4275.
METHOD     (ACTIV)
CORRECTION Corrected for
            . gamma-ray self-absorption
            . cascade decay
            . counting geometry
            . neutron fluence fluctuation
STATUS     (TABLE,,Kong Xiangzhong+,J,CNP,14,239,1992) Table 2
HISTORY    (19930125C) Compiled by Liang Qichang (CNDC)
           (20100807A) SD: ERR-9 -> EN-ERR in all Subents
           (20240216U) On. REFERENCE(CNP): Issue number deleted.
           (20260409A) VT. Entry revised
ENDBIB              27
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           30
