REACTION   (42-MO-98(N,A)40-ZR-95,,SIG)
DECAY-DATA (40-ZR-95,64.02D,DG,756.729,0.2413)
SAMPLE     Natural metal foil of Mo, diameter was 20 mm, the
           thickness was 0.2 mm and the purity was 99.99%.
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-T) The major uncertainties of the results
                   are as follows:
           (ERR-S,0.5,0.7) Statistics for residual nuclides
                           (0.5-0.7%)
           (ERR-1) Detector efficiency for residual nuclides(1.5)
           (ERR-2) Detector efficiency for Na-24 (1.5%)
           (MONIT-ERR,1.2,1.5) Cross section for Al-27(n,a)Na-24
                           (1.2-1.5%)
           (DATA-ERR,0.5,0.6) Statistics for Na-24 (0.5-0.6%)
           (ERR-3) Gamma-ray self-absorption in sample (1.0%)
           (ERR-4) Gamma-ray self-absorption in Na-24 (1.0%)
           (ERR-5) Geometry of sample (1.0%)
           (ERR-6) Geometry of Na-24 (1.0%)
           (ERR-7) Sample purity (0.1%)
           (ERR-8) Al-27 purity (0.15%)
           (EN-ERR) Neutron energy (0.4%)
MONITOR    (13-AL-27(N,A)11-NA-24,,SIG) Natural metal foil of Al,
           the diameter was 20 mm, the thickness 0.1 mm and the
           purity 99.999%.
DECAY-MON  (11-NA-24,14.956HR,DG,1368.598,1.)
